<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="MTA65">
<l>viṉaiyā laṭarppaṭār vennarakiṟ cērār</l>
<l>tiṉaiyēṉun tīkkatikkaṭ cellār – niṉaitaṟ</l>
<l>kariyāṉaic cēyāṉai yāyirampērc ceṅkaṭ</l>
<l>kariyāṉaik kaitoḻutak kāl.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>They shall not be oppressed by karma, they shall not join hot hell,</l>
<l>they shall not, even by a trifle, go on evil paths – when they [fold</l> 
<l>their] hands in worship of the black one with red eyes, with a thousand names, </l>
<l>the distant one, the one who is difficult to think of.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
